name: Object

name: Function
description: A Function is a block of code designed to perform a particular task when invoked.

name: Callback Function
description: A callback function is a function passed into another function as an argument, which is then called inside the outer function to perform a particular task.

name: Properties
description: Properties are the most important part of any JavaScript object. often describing attributes associated with a data structure.

name: class
description: A class is a type of function, but instead of using the keyword function to initiate it, we use the keyword class, and the properties are assigned inside a constructor() method.

name: Expression
description: An expression is a combination of values, variables, and operators, which evaluates to a value.

name: Array
description: An array is a special variable, which can hold more than one value at a time

name: Variable
description: Variable is a container for storing data to be referenced and manipulated

name: SQL
description: SQL stands for Structured Query Language for accessing database

name: Props
description: Props are arguments passed into React components.

name: React
description: React is an open-source JavaScript library created by Facebook for building user interfaces

name: Render
description: Render is the process of transforming the JSX of your react component into a DOM element that your browser can understand.

name: React Components
description: Components are independent and reusable bits of code.There are two main types of components in React. Class Components and Functional Components.Class components are ES6 classes and Functional Components are functions

name: Regular expression
description: Regular expressions are patterns used to match character combinations in strings

name: Array forEach method
description: The forEach() method calls a function once for each element in an array, in order.

name: Array map method
description: The map() method creates a new array with the results of calling a function for every array element.
